name: Flohr - an es the ti ca - Interactive Album Art
description: The eight pieces that make up this album were performed and recorded live by Flohr on a Eurorack modular synthesizer in the period immediately following a near death experience in 2019. No midi involved, no other instruments, and no overdubs. Generative visuals were created to amplify the textural emotion in the piece. Experience the album, export new album art, and record excerpts in this software. *This includes a .toe file to run the app, & code is open source* dm:@thegladscientist 4 access
